Method Detail

load

public void load(File file)
Description copied from interface: PluginType
Load method that is called when a file that matches the extension specified is found in plugins directory. If this plugin requires manual adding (IE JavaPlugin) then it must set the name to null so it can be ignored

Implementations of this must completly setup the Plugin, parsing all avalible infomration. The plugin must then be able to be activated by PluginType.invoke(java.lang.String[], Quackbot.Bot, Quackbot.info.BotEvent)

Specified by:
load in interface PluginType
Parameters:
file - The file that contains the script
